WARNING: this is not a official OMD release!

   OMD - the Open Monitoring Distribution (New Cores Edition)
      <http://omdistro.org/> - <http://labs.consol.de

OMD with 2 new Cores: Naemon and Icinga 2. APIs have changed, new
Livestatus implementations have been build, so this build makes it
easier to test the new cores with Thruk and Mod-Gearman.


What OMD-NC contains in addition
--------------------------------

  * Naemon
  * Livestatus for Naemon
  * Mod-Gearman for Naemon
  * Icinga 2
  * PNP for Naemon
  * Best Practices:
    - Thruk
      - set as default gui
      - autostart enabled
      - enable cookie authentication
    - Naemon
      - enabled by default

